---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Software para clínica dental en Perú | AgendaDr"
  description="Software odontológico con planes de tratamiento multi-fase, cobros Yape, CRM WhatsApp y portal de pacientes. Para dentistas y clínicas dentales. Desde S/49/mes."
>
  <Header />
  <main>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">
          <span class="specialty-badge">🦷 Odontología</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-headline">El software que tu clínica dental<br class="dbr"> estaba esperando.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Agenda citas, gestiona planes de tratamiento de ortodoncia, cobra con Yape al agendar y deja que tus pacientes vean el progreso de sus brackets desde su portal. Todo en AgendaDr.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="https://app.agendadr.com/registro" class="btn-primary">Empieza desde S/49/mes →</a>
          <a href="/demo" class="btn-ghost">Pide una demo gratis</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <span>✅ 14 días gratis</span>
          <span>✅ Sin tarjeta de crédito</span>
          <span>✅ Onboarding incluido</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Decoración fondo -->
      <div class="hero-deco" aria-hidden="true">🦷</div>
    </section>

    <!-- POR QUÉ ODONTOLOGÍA + AGENDADR -->
    <section class="features-section anim-fade-up">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Por qué odontología + AgendaDr</span>
          <h2>Diseñado para la realidad de una clínica dental.</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">Cada función fue pensada para los problemas reales que enfrenta un dentista en Perú.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">

          <div class="feat-card anim-item">
            <div class="feat-icon">📋</div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <h3>Planes de tratamiento multi-fase</h3>
              <p>Brackets metálicos, cerámicos, implantes, endodoncia. Crea el plan con fases, genera citas automáticas. Tu paciente ve en qué fase va desde su portal.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feat-card anim-item">
            <div class="feat-icon">💰</div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <h3>Ticket expandible</h3>
              <p>El paciente viene por limpieza (S/80) y le detectas caries → curación (S/120) → brackets (S/2,500). Agregas servicios del catálogo durante la consulta. El ticket se triplica.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feat-card anim-item">
            <div class="feat-icon">📱</div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <h3>Cobros con Yape y Plin</h3>
              <p>Tu paciente agenda online y paga con Yape. No más cobros en efectivo ni perseguir pagos después de la consulta.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feat-card anim-item">
            <div class="feat-icon">💼</div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <h3>Comisiones automáticas</h3>
              <p>Si tienes varios odontólogos, las comisiones se calculan solas: bruto, comisión, neto. Sin Excel. Sin discusiones a fin de mes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feat-card anim-item">
            <div class="feat-icon">💬</div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <h3>CRM WhatsApp</h3>
              <p>Los leads de tus anuncios de Instagram llegan al panel de tu recepcionista. Responde y agenda sin salir del sistema. Ningún lead se pierde.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feat-card anim-item">
            <div class="feat-icon">🌐</div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <h3>Portal de pacientes</h3>
              <p>Tu paciente de ortodoncia ve sus citas, su plan de tratamiento con fases, descarga recetas y reagenda sin llamar. Tú te liberas del teléfono.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CASO DE USO -->
    <section class="case-section anim-fade-up">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
          <div class="case-content">
            <div class="case-tag">Caso real</div>
            <p class="case-text">La Dra. García tiene una clínica dental con 3 odontólogos. Cada uno atiende 12 pacientes al día. Antes usaban cuadernos y WhatsApp personal. Ahora los pacientes agendan solos, pagan con Yape, y el dashboard le muestra cuánto facturó cada doctor. Las comisiones se calculan solas y los pacientes de ortodoncia siguen su plan desde el portal.</p>
            <div class="case-author">
              <div class="case-avatar">🦷</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Dra. García</strong>
                <span>Directora — Clínica Dental García, Lima</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="case-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-val">3x</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Ticket promedio</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-val">0</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Cobros en efectivo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-val">100%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Comisiones automáticas</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PLAN RECOMENDADO -->
    <section class="plan-section anim-fade-up">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Planes</span>
          <h2>Elige el plan que se adapta a tu clínica dental.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="plans-row">

          <div class="plan-card anim-item">
            <div class="plan-for">Solo o 1 dentista</div>
            <div class="plan-name">Individual</div>
            <div class="plan-price"><span class="price-amount">S/49</span><span class="price-period">/mes</span></div>
            <ul class="plan-features">
              <li>✓ Agenda online 24/7</li>
              <li>✓ Historial médico</li>
              <li>✓ Recetas digitales</li>
              <li>✓ Cobros con Yape y Plin</li>
              <li>✓ Recordatorios WhatsApp</li>
              <li>✓ Portal de pacientes</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://app.agendadr.com/registro" class="plan-cta plan-cta-ghost">Empezar gratis →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="plan-card plan-featured anim-item">
            <div class="plan-badge">Recomendado para clínicas</div>
            <div class="plan-for">2–5 dentistas</div>
            <div class="plan-name">Básico</div>
            <div class="plan-price"><span class="price-amount">S/149</span><span class="price-period">/mes</span></div>
            <ul class="plan-features">
              <li>✓ Todo lo del plan Individual</li>
              <li>✓ Planes de tratamiento multi-fase</li>
              <li>✓ Comisiones automáticas</li>
              <li>✓ CRM WhatsApp</li>
              <li>✓ Reportes de ingresos por doctor</li>
              <li>✓ Hasta 5 usuarios</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://app.agendadr.com/registro" class="plan-cta plan-cta-primary">Empezar gratis →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="plan-card anim-item">
            <div class="plan-for">Clínica grande o red</div>
            <div class="plan-name">Profesional</div>
            <div class="plan-price"><span class="price-amount">S/299</span><span class="price-period">/mes</span></div>
            <ul class="plan-features">
              <li>✓ Todo lo del plan Básico</li>
              <li>✓ Multi-sede</li>
              <li>✓ White-label (tu marca)</li>
              <li>✓ Reportes avanzados</li>
              <li>✓ API de integración</li>
              <li>✓ Usuarios ilimitados</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/demo" class="plan-cta plan-cta-ghost">Hablar con ventas →</a>
          </div>

        </div>
        <p class="plans-note">Todos los planes incluyen 14 días de prueba gratuita · Sin contrato · Cancela cuando quieras</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA FINAL -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-card">
          <div class="cta-icon" aria-hidden="true">🦷</div>
          <h2 class="cta-headline">Tu clínica dental merece un sistema moderno.</h2>
          <p class="cta-sub">Únete a los dentistas que ya digitalizaron su práctica con AgendaDr.</p>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a href="https://app.agendadr.com/registro" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Empieza desde S/49/mes →</a>
            <a href="/demo" class="btn-ghost btn-lg">Ver demo en vivo</a>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-links">
            <a href="/especialidades">← Ver todas las especialidades</a>
            <span>·</span>
            <a href="/planes">Ver todos los planes →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Tokens ── */
  :root {
    --green: #03BB85;
    --green-dark: #029e70;
    --green-light: rgba(3,187,133,0.1);
    --bg-page: #ffffff;
    --bg-subtle: #f8fafc;
    --text-heading: #0f172a;
    --text-secondary: #334155;
    --text-muted: #64748b;
    --border: #e2e8f0;
  }
  :global(html.dark) {
    --bg-page: #0f172a;
    --bg-subtle: #1e293b;
    --text-heading: #f1f5f9;
    --text-secondary: #cbd5e1;
    --text-muted: #94a3b8;
    --border: #334155;
  }

  /* ── Reset base ── */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  main { background: var(--bg-page); }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { padding: 0 16px; } }

  .dbr { display: none; }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .dbr { display: block; } }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 140px 0 96px;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf9 0%, #ffffff 70%);
  }
  :global(html.dark) .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(3,187,133,0.06) 0%, var(--bg-page) 70%);
  }

  .hero-deco {
    position: absolute;
    top: 48px;
    right: 8%;
    font-size: 120px;
    opacity: 0.06;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    transform: rotate(15deg);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-deco { display: none; } }

  .hero-eyebrow { margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .specialty-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: #ecfdf5;
    color: #059669;
    border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  :global(html.dark) .specialty-badge {
    background: rgba(3,187,133,0.1);
    color: #34d399;
    border-color: rgba(3,187,133,0.25);
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 36px;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ── Buttons ── */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.12s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(3,187,133,0.35);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--green-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(3,187,133,0.45); }
  .btn-primary.btn-lg { font-size: 16px; padding: 15px 32px; }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 13px 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); background: var(--green-light); }
  .btn-ghost.btn-lg { font-size: 16px; padding: 15px 28px; }

  /* ── Section shared ── */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }
  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── FEATURES ── */
  .features-section {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: var(--bg-page);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .features-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .feat-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--bg-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .feat-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(3,187,133,0.12);
    border-color: rgba(3,187,133,0.3);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .feat-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .feat-body h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .feat-body p {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── CASO DE USO ── */
  .case-section {
    padding: 0 0 96px;
    background: var(--bg-page);
  }

  .case-card {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf9 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
    border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  :global(html.dark) .case-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(3,187,133,0.06) 0%, rgba(3,187,133,0.1) 100%);
    border-color: rgba(3,187,133,0.22);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .case-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 28px 24px; gap: 28px; }
  }

  .case-quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    left: 28px;
    font-size: 100px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--green);
    opacity: 0.12;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .case-content { position: relative; }
  .case-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #059669;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  :global(html.dark) .case-tag { color: #34d399; }

  .case-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .case-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .case-avatar {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: #dcfce7;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  :global(html.dark) .case-avatar { background: rgba(3,187,133,0.15); }
  .case-author strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }
  .case-author span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .case-metrics {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .case-metrics { flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-around; }
  }
  .metric {
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    min-width: 120px;
  }
  :global(html.dark) .metric { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-color: rgba(3,187,133,0.22); }
  .metric-val {
    display: block;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .metric-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* ── PLAN SECTION ── */
  .plan-section {
    padding: 0 0 96px;
    background: var(--bg-page);
  }

  .plans-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .plans-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; } }

  .plan-card {
    background: var(--bg-subtle);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .plan-card.plan-featured {
    background: #fff;
    border-color: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--green), 0 8px 32px rgba(3,187,133,0.15);
  }
  :global(html.dark) .plan-card.plan-featured {
    background: rgba(3,187,133,0.06);
  }

  .plan-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -13px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .plan-for {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .plan-name {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }
  .plan-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 2px; }
  .price-amount {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .price-period { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  .plan-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .plan-features li {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .plan-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 11px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .plan-cta-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(3,187,133,0.3);
  }
  .plan-cta-primary:hover { background: var(--green-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .plan-cta-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
  }
  .plan-cta-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); background: var(--green-light); }

  .plans-note {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ── CTA FINAL ── */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 0 0 96px;
    background: var(--bg-page);
  }
  .cta-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 64px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  :global(html.dark) .cta-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
    border: 1px solid #334155;
  }

  .cta-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  .cta-headline {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cta-card .btn-ghost {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    border-color: #475569;
  }
  .cta-card .btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--green);
    color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(3,187,133,0.1);
  }
  .cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .cta-links a { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s; }
  .cta-links a:hover { color: var(--green); }
  .cta-links span { color: #334155; }

  /* ── Animaciones ── */
  .anim-fade-up { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.55s ease, transform 0.55s ease; }
  .anim-fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .anim-item { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.45s ease, transform 0.45s ease; }
  .anim-item.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .anim-fade-up, .anim-item { opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: none; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // IntersectionObserver para animaciones
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
      entry.target.classList.add('visible');
      const items = entry.target.querySelectorAll('.anim-item');
      items.forEach((el, i) => {
        setTimeout(() => el.classList.add('visible'), i * 80);
      });
      io.unobserve(entry.target);
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.08 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.anim-fade-up').forEach(el => io.observe(el));
</script>
